[research-costs] Research Costs (notstarted)
Gather estimates for materials, labor, permits, and land preparation.
Get quotes from at least three suppliers and two contractors.
---
[financing] Secure Financing (notstarted)
Apply for a construction loan, personal loan, RV loan, or arrange self-funding.
-> research-costs
> RV loans may apply if the home is on a trailer and RVIA-certified.
---
[cost-breakdown] Create Cost Breakdown (notstarted)
Build a detailed spreadsheet with line items for every phase.
Include a 15–20% contingency buffer for unexpected expenses.
-> research-costs
-> financing
