[floor-plan] Floor Plan Layout (notstarted)
Choose square footage, room layout, loft configuration, and storage strategy.
Consider traffic flow, natural light, and multi-use furniture placement.
---
[structural-plans] Structural & Engineering Plans (notstarted)
Hire a designer or purchase pre-made plans; obtain stamped structural drawings for permitting.
-> floor-plan
---
[material-selection] Material Selection (notstarted)
Choose framing lumber, roofing, siding, insulation type, windows, and finish materials.
Balance cost, weight (critical for trailer builds), and durability.
-> floor-plan
-> cost-breakdown
