---
[zoning-research] Zoning & Code Research (notstarted)
Confirm the lot is zoned for a tiny home or ADU and check minimum size requirements.
Review setback rules, height limits, and any HOA restrictions.
---
[building-permit] Apply for Building Permit (notstarted)
Submit plans and applications to the local building department.
Allow 2–8 weeks for review depending on jurisdiction.
